item.title: CVE-2016-1203|2024-09-06T20:15:41.041Z -- netmove%20corporation -- saat%20netizen%20installer
item.description: Improper file verification vulnerability in SaAT Netizen installer ver.1.2.0.424 and earlier, and SaAT Netizen ver.1.2.0.8 (Build427) and earlier allows a remote unauthenticated attacker to conduct a man-in-the-middle attack. A successful exploitation may result in a malicious file being downloaded and executed.
